"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"### \\n\\n> ### Binance code introduction\\n>\\n> Binance Code allows simple crypto transfer and exchange through secured and prepaid codes that give access to crypto assets. Binance Code API solution is to facilitate instant creation, redemption and value-checking for Binance Codes. Binance code consists of two parts: Reference number and Binance code. The reference number can circulate in public, and it can be used to verify the validity of the code; Binance Code should be kept carefully, because as long as someone has the code, they can redeem it  anytime.\\n\\n## 1. Create a Binance Code\\n\\n```\\nPOST /sapi/v1/giftcard/createCode\\n```\\n\\nThis API is for creating a Binance Code.\\n\\n*To get started with, please make sure:*\\n\\n*a. You have a Binance account*\\n\\n*b. You have passed kyc*\\n\\n*c. You have a sufﬁcient balance in your Binance funding wallet*\\n\\n**General** **Limitation** **(By** **Default)**：\\n\\nDaily creation volume: 2 BTC / 24H\\n\\nDaily creation times: 200 Codes / 24H\\n\\n**Parameter** **explanation**：\\n\\n1\\\\.  token: the coin type contained in the Binance Code\\n\\n2\\\\.  amount: the amount of the coin\\n\\n> Body parameter\\n\\n```\\n{\\n\\\"amount\\\": 0,\\n\\\"token\\\": \\\"string\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Parameters**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/E-0M1G6PqV3msvmq60k6I.png?height=804&width=1926)\\n\\n> Example responses\\n\\n**Responses**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/X0rZycxgWH-F_tEdyc1ft.png?height=944&width=1912)\\n\\n## 2. Redeem a Binance Code\\n\\n```\\nPOST /sapi/v1/giftcard/redeemCode\\n```\\n\\nThis API is for redeeming the Binance Code.\\n\\nOnce redeemed, the coins will be deposited in your funding wallet.\\n\\n**Please** **note** **that** **if** **you** **enter** **the** **wrong** **code** **5** **times** **within** **24** **hours,** **you** **will** **no** **longer** **be** **able** **to** **redeem** **any** **Binance** **Code** **that** **day.**\\n\\n> Body parameter\\n\\n```\\n{\\n\\n\\\"code\\\": \\\"string\\\"\\n\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Parameters**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fjTBhdLTfAXOJ07OdzycB.png?height=790&width=1900)\\n\\n> Example responses\\n\\n**Responses**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ilJNh141r4r_fC2aUj6TI.png?height=940&width=2024)\\n\\n## 3. Verify Binance Code\\n\\n```\\nGET /sapi/v1/giftcard/verify\\n```\\n\\nThis API is for verifying whether the Binance Code is valid or not by entering Binance Code or reference number.\\n\\n**Please** **note** **that** **if** **you** **enter** **the** **wrong** **binance** **code** **5** **times** **within** **an** **hour,** **you** **will** **no** **longer** **be** **able** **to** **verify** **any** **binance** **code** **for** **that** **hour.**\\n\\n**Parameters**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/eZbKb-q8ywyKxhfgFaeyQ.png?height=834&width=1910)\\n\\n> Example responses\\n\\n**Responses**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/atmLcexskhl1AN3NyvEnO.png?height=832&width=2124)\\n\\n### CommonRetRedeemBinanceCodeResponseInformation\\n\\n```\\n {\\r\\n\\\"code\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"data\\\": {\\r\\n\\\"referenceNo\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"identityNo\\\": \\\"string\\\"\\r\\n},\\r\\n\\\"message\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"success\\\": true\\r\\n}\\n```\\n\\n \\n **Properties**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jlcfKcAMyihXISYSGAWmb.png?height=540&width=1852)\\n\\n### CommonRetResponseForCreatingABinanceCode\\n\\n```\\n {\\r\\n\\\"code\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"data\\\": {\\r\\n\\\"code\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"referenceNo\\\": \\\"string\\\"\\r\\n},\\r\\n\\\"message\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"success\\\": true\\r\\n}\\n```\\n\\n \\n **Properties**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/U4b_2GV3MfHW_DsI9lyjm.png?height=534&width=1856)\\n\\n### CommonRetReponseToIdentifyWhetherTheBinanceCodeIsValid\\n\\n```\\n{\\r\\n\\\"code\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"data\\\": {\\r\\n\\\"valid\\\": true\\r\\n},\\r\\n\\\"message\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\r\\n\\\"success\\\": true\\r\\n}\\n```\\n\\n \\n **Properties**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/EpzcOJjezLKhlyDzMgtWo.png?height=554&width=1908)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642001627,\"title\":\"Binance Code SAPI\"},\"digest\":\"ljlcxN6TDKVhknsJlpHOHuRgiTClIJxakE8Uc5ehxlE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7E7cd4963299A38396d0E45f3BAAc4DB11421511\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ujejfSo5vDTGWlv-nuupgpXPJdg5qkSZnJJk1uS0SDA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JKapX7QQZT0CUE36aLXXEf3QHGjC7zoVDgZlNzugjkc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"siVsORqJPm7n33HhSKYOfyN5DreIMyEXjUr_tNrKeHtWh-KYR8KWmrp-PKOGaOo8uX2IOD9a1TsyXREu1Uci9Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x137ef13b20edd489cc3bd370f6a9d7b2df606071a724a2820a36f2c9f3a12d7a5a1631b9fda3632be4b85cc773be0c788264928a58ec6623b9c4662a078c15b11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ujejfSo5vDTGWlv-nuupgpXPJdg5qkSZnJJk1uS0SDA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JKapX7QQZT0CUE36aLXXEf3QHGjC7zoVDgZlNzugjkc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"absPX0mQ9f-Fm_9GzM63SrJp5Wqk8n8YQ2Gl4bjWXPE\"}"